If all the ranks are distinct (i.e. no ties) the formula can also be written as:

\deqn{r_s = 1 - \frac{6}{n\times\left(n^2 - 1\right)}\times S}
With:
\deqn{S = \sum_{i=1}^n d_i^2}
\deqn{d_i^2 = \left(r_{x_i} - r_{y_i}\right)^2}

